# Customer docs site — optional overrides only.
# Defaults are always https://api.salanor.com and https://console.salanor.com
# (never localhost), even when running `pnpm dev:docs` from the monorepo.
#
# Do NOT set NEXT_PUBLIC_AEGIS_API_URL here — that is for web-console only.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_DOCS_API_URL=https://api.salanor.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DOCS_CONSOLE_URL=https://console.salanor.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DOCS_MARKETING_URL=https://salanor.com
